\c 33 Erihu anotuka Jobho, Mwari haazi muvengi wavanhu, asi anovadzidzisa nemitowo mizhinji 1 Asi Jobho, chidonzwai henyu kutaura kwangu, Teererai mashoko angu ose. 2 Tarirai zvino, ndashamisa muromo wangu, Rurimi angu rw ataura mumuromo wangu, 3 Mashoko angu achadudzira kururama kwomwoyo wangu; Miromo yangu ichataura izvo zvainoziva nezvokwadi.
